WEBVTT

00:02.291 --> 00:05.522
I am the goddamn mayor
of this motherfucking city!

00:05.556 --> 00:08.029
And I want this hole fixed now!

00:08.465 --> 00:11.823
Mr. Langley has previously
undiagnosed open-angle glaucoma.

00:11.857 --> 00:14.242
- <i>To take that shot...</i>
- Motherfucker.

00:14.276 --> 00:16.096
- Where'd you get the urine?
- I don't understand.

00:16.131 --> 00:18.816
Bulbocapnine... used to
induce a severe stupor.

00:18.851 --> 00:20.745
Grandpa, did they do this to you?

00:20.779 --> 00:22.341
Hell no, we won't go!

00:22.375 --> 00:25.640
Mr. Zajac is this an attempt to get
back into your wife's good graces?

00:26.175 --> 00:27.176
Don't resist.

00:29.007 --> 00:30.115
I love you.

00:30.149 --> 00:32.253
- Where is the mayor?
- You'll be apprised soon enough.

00:32.287 --> 00:34.128
Until then, I believe
you have a job to perform.

00:34.663 --> 00:36.404
You have been paid,

00:36.438 --> 00:38.920
so may we start the fucking
treatment, please?

00:38.954 --> 00:41.940
With the first injection,
the pain may be sharp.

00:41.975 --> 00:44.796
After hours of seemingly
unending violence,

00:44.831 --> 00:47.923
<i>the toll of injury</i>
<i>and destruction is growing.</i>

00:48.207 --> 00:50.525
CPD shot an unarmed kid.

00:50.543 --> 00:52.988
We've always had
a mutual respect, Mac.

00:53.022 --> 00:55.009
We have, you being cut from the
same cloth as your father.

00:55.043 --> 00:57.409
20 years ago, we urged Tom to ask

00:57.443 --> 00:59.255
<i>for a deployment</i>
<i>of the National Guard.</i>

00:59.290 --> 01:00.746
I'd like to hear it from him.

01:00.780 --> 01:02.304
You will, in due time.

01:02.338 --> 01:03.617
- Sam.
- <i>Yeah?</i>

01:03.651 --> 01:05.576
The papers on your table, Rosebud.

01:05.611 --> 01:07.970
<i>I'm pretty sure the</i>
<i>handwriting's Stone's.</i>

